      "content": "Hey, I'm working on the Q4 strategy for a high-end heritage watch brand—think Patek level. We need to refine our target persona for the new global campaign. Can you help me build out a detailed profile of the 'ideal consumer'? I need specifics on their lifestyle, interests, and especially their cultural and ethnic background to make sure our imagery and placement feel authentic to that high-net-worth demographic.",
